329
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:47,100
What, that the credit card
was canceled by my lover's mommy?

330
00:19:47,100 --> 00:19:49,000
Well, what other options do you have?

331
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:51,100
Unless you return the shoes
and get the money back.

332
00:19:51,100 --> 00:19:53,600
Return the shoes?

333
00:19:53,600 --> 00:19:56,700
I can't talk to you
when you're being hysterical.

334
00:19:58,500 --> 00:20:03,100
So, ma'am, what would you
like to do about the bill?

335
00:20:15,100 --> 00:20:18,300
Afternoon. I've got a package
for your neighbor Karen Mccluskey.

336
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:19,400
You mind signing?

337
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:21,200
